	<summary>Timer and Alarm</summary>
	<description>
		<p>A simple standalone Timer and Alarm. </p>
		<p>1. Set time</p>
		<p>right click on the surface of clock, set the alarm time.</p>
		<p>In the center part, roll up to increase timing minutes.</p>
		<p>2. Start</p>
		<p>Click the center to activate.</p>
		<p>Right click the center to exit.</p>
